  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Cargo storage components provide storage for cargo while
  being transported or stored</span>.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>These are typically used on space ports and mining
  stations to store resources and components for later use. They are also u=
sed
  on freighter ships or mining ships to transport resources between locatio=
ns.
  Construction ships also require storage components to temporarily store
  resources and components when building new bases.<span lang=3DEN-GB
  style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'><o:p></o:p></span></p>
